cs.MM, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.SY

The paper deals with quality adaptation algorithms for adaptive bitrate (ABR) video streaming, which involves machine learning and network infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves decision-making under uncertainty, which falls under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
